BoundaryAlignmentToClassificationFactory - Class in net.sourceforge.nite.datainspection.timespan
Given two aligned boundary lists, make two calc.Classification as follows:
1) All Pairs of aligned boundaries are Items; the Value for both annotators is True
2) For each unaligned boundary a Pair is made as Item with the unaligned boundary, and a null for the other annotator; the Values for this Item are True for the annotator who DID find a boundary, and False for the other.

Implements distance of interface DistanceMetric distance(v1,v2) = 1.0 if (v1.datype != v2.datype) distance(v1,v2) = lambda * distance(v1.aset,v2.aset) + (1-lambda)*distance(v1.bset,v2.bset) User can set the lambda value but it should be in [0,1] using Dice coefficient on two given sets
distance(Value, Value) - Method in class net.sourceforge.nite.datainspection.impl.DiceMetricsForTwoSetValues

makeClassification(List, List, NOMElementToValueDelegate) - Static method in class net.sourceforge.nite.datainspection.timespan.TimelineDiscretizationClassificationFactory
Given the list of Items generated by generateDiscretizedItems, and a segmentlist, and a NomElementToValueDelegate, generate a Classification.
makeClassificationsFromAlignments(BoundaryAlignment) - Static method in class net.sourceforge.nite.datainspection.timespan.BoundaryAlignmentToClassificationFactory
Given two aligned boundary lists, make two calc.Classification as follows:
1) All Pairs of aligned boundaries are Items; the Value for both annotators is True
2) For each unaligned boundary a Pair is made as Item with the unaligned boundary, and a null for the other annotator; the Values for this Item are True for the annotator who DID find a boundary, and False for the other.
makeClassificationsFromAlignments(SegmentAlignment, NOMElementToValueDelegate) - Static method in class net.sourceforge.nite.datainspection.timespan.SegmentAlignmentToClassificationFactory
Given two aligned segment lists, make two calc.Classification where all Pairs of aligned segments are Items; and the Values are determined by the NOMElementToValueDelegate.
makeClassificationsFromBoundaryList(List, List) - Static method in class net.sourceforge.nite.datainspection.timespan.DiscretizationBasedBoundaryToClassificationFactory
